name: Collectd-plot
body:
### Collectd-Plot

A shard-aware web-UI and API to expose Collectd time-series data.

#### Quick start:

```
$ git clone git@github.com:echohead/collectd-plot.git
$ cd collectd-plot
$ vagrant up
< point browser to http://localhost:8081 >
```
